{"abstract":[{"text":"Discover how you can use App Sandbox to protect your app’s users from unintentional bugs or deliberate attempts to compromise security. Understand sandboxing’s security goals, how applications and their data are isolated from each other, and how to express the resources your application needs. Learn about App Sandbox-related APIs and entitlements, and how to adopt them for your app to meet the Mac App Store Guidelines.","type":"text"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2013\/710\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}},"kind":"article","identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC13-710-A-Practical-Guide-to-the-App-Sandbox"},"sections":[],"metadata":{"role":"sampleCode","roleHeading":"WWDC13","title":"A Practical Guide to the App Sandbox","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc13-710-a-practical-guide-to-the-app-sandbox"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC13"]]},"references":{"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2013/710/":{"type":"download","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2013\/710\/","identi